text: Jay Prakash Singh Bhogta was the state legislative assembly member from Chatra. He is a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. In the 2014 general election, he was elected as MLA of Chatra. His father Mahendra Prakash Singh Bhogta was MLA of Chatra. == References == Category:Living people Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Jharkhand Category:Jharkhand MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Chatra district Category:Jharkhand Vikas Morcha (Prajatantrik) politicians
